Title : Lagadin
Text : '''Lagadin''' ({{lang-mk|Лагадин}}) is a small tourist village in the [[Republic of North Macedonia]], located 9 kilometres south of the city of [[Ohrid]]. It is a popular beachside destination along [[Lake Ohrid]] and lies at the foot of [[Galičica]] National Park.

